            </div>

             <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="BiographyMatthew">
                <label>Biography of Matthew</label>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>ወለማቴዎስ፡ ስሙ፡ ሌዊ፡ ወትርጓሜሁ፡ ኅሩይ፡ ወውእቱ፡
                 እምነገደ፡ ይሳኮር፡ እምሀገረ፡ ናዝሬት። ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ዲቁ፡ ወስመ፡ እሙ፡ ካሩትያስ።</ab></div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወሰበከ፡ ባቲ፡ በህንድ፡ ወበኢየሩሳሌም።</ab></div>
             </div>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="EusebianSectionsMatthew">
                <label>Statement about the Eusebian Sections in the Gospel of Matthew</label>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>ወኍልቈ፡ ምዕራፋቲሁ፡ ንኡሳን፡ ፫፻፶፭፡</ab></div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወምዕራፉ፡ በልሳነ፡ ሮሜ። ፷፰፡</ab></div>
             </div>
             <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="TituliMatthew">
                <label>Tituli of the Gospel of Matthew</label>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>
                <l n="1">፩፡ ሰብአ፡ ሰገል።</l>
                <l n="2">፪፡ ቅትለተ፡ ሕፃናት።</l>
                <l n="3">፫፡ ስብከተ፡ ዮሓንስ።</l></ab></div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>
                <l n="66">፷፮፡ ክሕደተ፡ ጴጥሮስ።</l>
                <l n="67">፷፯፡ ነስሖተ፡ ይሁዳ።</l>
                <l n="68">፷፰፡ ዘከመ፡ ነሥአ፡ ዮሴፍ፡ ራማዊ፡ ሥጋሁ፡ ለእግዚእ።</l></ab></div>
              </div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2709Matthew">
                <label>Bǝsrāta Mātewos</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="subtextunit" xml:id="MatthewGospelHeadline">
                 <label>Headline of the Gospel of Matthew</label>
                  <ab>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩፡ አምላክ። <seg type="title inscriptio expanded">ብስራተ፡ ወንጌል፡
                   ማቴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ። አሓዱ፡ እምዓሠርቱ፡ ወክልኤቱ።</seg> ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብሩ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="Abr"/>
                    ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="coretext" xml:id="MatthewGospel">
                  <label>Gospel of Matthew</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>መጽሐፈ፡ ልደቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ።
                  ወልደ፡ ዳዊት፡ ወልደ፡ አብርሃም። አብርሃምኒ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለይስሓቅ። ወይስሓቅኒ፡ ወለዶ፡ ለያዕቆብ።</ab></div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>ወናሁ፡ አነ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ ምስሌክሙ፡ በኵሉ፡ መዋዕል፡ እስከ፡
                  ኅልቀተ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</ab></div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="colophon" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="PostscriptMatthew">
                  <label>Colophon of the Gospel of Matthew</label>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>መልአ፡ ጽሕፈተ፡ <seg type="title subscriptio">ብስራቱ፡
                  ለማቴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ።</seg> ወኮነ፡ ጸሓፎ፡ በምድረ፡ ፍልስጥዔም፡</ab></div>
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>በቀዳሚሁ፡
                  ዓ<choice><sic>ም</sic><corr resp="ABr">መ</corr></choice><supplied reason="omitted" resp="ABr">ተ</supplied>፡
                  እምቀላውዴዎስ፡ ቄሳር፡ ንጉሠ፡ ሮሜ። ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብሩ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="Abr"/>
                  ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</ab></div>
                </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
